#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:35
msgid "Create announcement"
msgstr "お知らせを作成"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:42
msgid "Create a course announcement. The announcement is attached to a course and supports scheduling and visibility control."
msgstr "コースのお知らせを作成します。お知らせはコースに紐付き、スケジュール設定と公開範囲の制御に対応します。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:55
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementGetTool.php:73
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementUpdateTool.php:60
msgid "The announcement title."
msgstr "お知らせのタイトル。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:60
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementUpdateTool.php:78
msgid "The course ID this announcement belongs to. Must be a valid course product."
msgstr "このお知らせが属するコース ID。有効なコース商品である必要があります。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:64
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementUpdateTool.php:64
msgid "The announcement content. Allows the same HTML as a WordPress post."
msgstr "お知らせの本文。WordPress 投稿と同じ HTML を使用できます。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:70
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementUpdateTool.php:69
msgid "The post status. Use future together with a future post_date to schedule."
msgstr "投稿ステータス。future を未来の post_date と組み合わせるとスケジュール公開できます。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:74
msgid "The publish date (Y-m-d H:i:s, site timezone). Defaults to now."
msgstr "公開日時（Y-m-d H:i:s、サイトのタイムゾーン）。既定値は現在時刻。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:80
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementGetTool.php:93
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementUpdateTool.php:83
msgid "Visibility: public (everyone) or enrolled (purchasers only)."
msgstr "公開範囲：public（全員）または enrolled（購入者のみ）。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:84
msgid "Expiration time as a 10-digit Unix timestamp, must be later than post_date. Leave empty to never expire."
msgstr "有効期限（10 桁の Unix タイムスタンプ）。post_date より後である必要があります。空にすると無期限になります。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:100
msgid "The ID of the newly created announcement."
msgstr "新しく作成されたお知らせの ID。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:135
msgid "post_title is a required field and cannot be empty."
msgstr "post_title は必須項目であり、空にはできません。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:142
msgid "parent_course_id is a required field and must be a positive integer."
msgstr "parent_course_id は必須項目であり、正の整数である必要があります。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementCreateTool.php:149
msgid "parent_course_id does not match an existing course product."
msgstr "parent_course_id に該当するコース商品が存在しません。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:34
msgid "Delete announcement"
msgstr "お知らせを削除"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:41
msgid "Delete a course announcement. By default the announcement is moved to trash; set force to true to permanently delete it."
msgstr "コースのお知らせを削除します。既定ではゴミ箱へ移動します。force を true にすると完全に削除します。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:54
msgid "The announcement ID to delete."
msgstr "削除するお知らせ ID。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:59
msgid "When true, permanently delete the announcement instead of moving it to trash."
msgstr "true の場合、ゴミ箱へ移動せずにお知らせを完全に削除します。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:75
msgid "Whether the announcement was deleted successfully."
msgstr "お知らせが正常に削除されたかどうか。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:79
msgid "The deleted announcement ID."
msgstr "削除されたお知らせの ID。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:83
msgid "Whether the deletion was permanent."
msgstr "完全削除かどうか。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:115
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementGetTool.php:133
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementUpdateTool.php:136
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/ContactRemark/ContactRemarkDeleteTool.php:110
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Email/EmailDeleteTool.php:106
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Email/EmailGetTool.php:116
#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Email/EmailUpdateTool.php:137
msgid "id is required and must be a positive integer."
msgstr "id は必須で、正の整数である必要があります。"

#: inc/classes/Api/Mcp/Tools/Announcement/AnnouncementDeleteTool.php:139
#: inc/classes/Resources/Announcement/Core/Api.php:185
